<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦٤٠٦]</span> أبو شَهْم <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عن:</span> أبي هريرة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عنه:</span> يحيى بن أبي كثير، وهو وَهمٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وصوابه:</span> أبو مسلم.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى له:</span> ابن ماجه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦٤٠٧]</span> أبو شَيْبَة <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عن:</span> عبد الله بن عُكَيْم.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عنه:</span> الجَرَّاح بن الضَّحّاك الكِنْديُّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روي له:</span> الترمذي.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>• أبو شَيْبَة،<span style="color:#006d98"> أظنه:</span> الجَوْهريُّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عن:</span> أنس بن مالك.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
